# Security Configuration for CoPA Stop & Search

# Exclude security report files from scanning (prevents recursive false positives)
security-reports/

# Exclude node_modules from secrets scanning
**/node_modules/**

# Exclude TypeScript definition files (often contain keywords that trigger false positives)
**/*.d.ts

# Exclude documentation and test files from critical security scanning
**/*.md
**/*.test.*
**/*.spec.*

# Exclude build artifacts
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.next/**

# Exclude package manager files (these are meant to be public)
package-lock.json
yarn.lock

# Exclude configuration files that may contain template values
**/*.example.*
**/*.template.*
